import React from "react";
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route } from "react-router-dom";
import "../styles/App.css";
import Navbar from "react-bootstrap/Navbar";
import Nav from "react-bootstrap/Nav";
import { LinkContainer } from 'react-router-bootstrap'
import NavItem from "react-bootstrap/esm/NavItem";

//components
import Abstract from "./Abstract"
import Database from "./Database"
import FastAPI from "./FastAPI"
import FrontEnd from "./FrontEnd"
import Scraper from "./Scraper"
import Footer from "./Footer";


function App() {
  return (
    <Router>
      <Navbar className="main-navbar" bg="light" expand="lg">
          <Navbar.Brand>Group 11</Navbar.Brand>
          <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
          <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
            <Nav className="mr-auto">
              <LinkContainer className="nav-link-text" to="/">
                <NavItem>Home</NavItem>
              </LinkContainer>
              <LinkContainer className="nav-link-text" to="/fastapi">
                <NavItem>View movies</NavItem>
              </LinkContainer>
              <LinkContainer className="nav-link-text" to="/database">
                <NavItem>Search Reactions</NavItem>
              </LinkContainer>
              <LinkContainer className="nav-link-text" to="/frontend">
                <NavItem>Audience segmentation</NavItem>
              </LinkContainer>
              <LinkContainer className="nav-link-text" to="/scraper">
                <NavItem>Future predictions</NavItem>
              </LinkContainer>
            </Nav>
          </Navbar.Collapse>
        </Navbar>

      <Switch className="main-content"> 
        <Route path="/database" component={Database} />
        <Route path="/frontend" component={FrontEnd} />
        <Route path="/scraper" component={Scraper} />
        <Route path="/fastapi" component={Abstract} />
        <Route path="" component={FastAPI} />
      </Switch>

    </Router>
  );
}

export default App;
